MainActivity - Class in ca.ualberta.app.activity
This is the mean activity that contains 5 mean functionalities by inflating 5 fragments: (1) view all questions authors have posted; (2) view users' favorite questions; (3) login as an author, and create a new question; (4) search questions which contain a given keyword; (5) view and modify user profiles.
